webLinks.linkText: The Hills Shire Council - Temporary Road Closures

properties.otherAdvice: Oversize and overmass (OSOM) vehicles should avoid the area and use an alternative route.
Visit the Council's website or social media channels for further information.

properties.headline: FLOODING WILCANNIA TO IVANHOE Cobb Highway CLOSED
properties.diversions:
Southbound from Wilcannia: Barrier Hwy to Cobar, Kidman Way to Goolgowi, and Mid Western Hwy to Hay.

Northbound from Hay: Mid Western Hwy to Goolgowi, Kidman Way to Cobar, and Barrier Hwy to Wilcannia.

This route is suitable for all vehicles and will add around 4hrs to your travel time.

properties.otherAdvice: Other local roads in the Forbes Shire Council area may be closed due to flooding or affected by recent adverse weather. Visit the council's website for further information.

properties.publicTransport: Visit transportnsw.info to plan your trip on public transport.

properties.headline: FLOODING WALGETT TO BREWARRINA Kamilaroi Highway
properties.otherAdvice: The road is flooded approximately 65km west of Walgett.
properties.diversions:
From Walgett to Bourke: Castlereagh Hwy to Gilgandra, Oxley Hwy to Nevertire, Mitchell Hwy to Bourke.

From Brewarrina to Bourke:: Arthur Hall Vc Way to Coolabah, then Mitchell Hwy to Bourke.


These diversions are suitable for all vehicles.

properties.otherAdvice: Delay non essential travel

Bourke to Walgett: Mitchell Hwy, Oxley Hwy, Castlereagh Hwy and vice versa.

Brewarrina to Walgett: Arthur Hall Vc Way, Mitchell Hwy, Oxley Hwy, Castlereagh Hwy and vice versa.
